data.description:
Must see rare, elegantly updated end unit townhouse with attached 2 car garage located in the coveted The Shores community. This is RESORT STYLE LIVING in the heart of Metro Denver!  Your main level windows showcase the private pond surrounded by an abundance of flowers and trees...relax while listening to the water feature and gazing at nature! Enjoy an abundance of amenities such as hot tub, tennis courts, sauna, trails with ponds and wildlife, indoor pool, outdoor pool, fitness center, game room with billiards, library, clubhouse and more! New double pane windows and patio sliding glass door!
Located in the acclaimed Cherry Creek school District, near the Cherry Creek Reservoir/State Park, Anschutz Medical Campus, Medical Center of Aurora, The Cherry Creek Trail and endless restaurants, shopping and outdoor activities! Convenient, quick access to RTD busses and light rail and close to downtown Denver and the Denver Tech Center!  Live, work and play all in one place with this welcoming community and beautiful townhome!
